      "id": "PopularPost356497",
      "post_content": "I love this card! Land D for the win! Screw your duals and your cradles and your coffers and your towers and tombs and towers. And those blasted all powerful guild gates. I usually set this up with a [vandal blast](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=vandal blast) to make sure i have ALL the advantage. [strip mine](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=strip mine) your one island in response!!  \n  \nOn the flip side I have decks with 0 basic lands. I'd hate to see this. But that's why I run counter spells. And [faith's reward](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=faith's reward). Because there's no kill like overkill.  \n  \n10/5!!! Print more playable land destruction! It's a necessary evil. And who needs friends?",
